And It Works! Thanks jmb!

The keygen works on the latest version as well, 9.5.1.7 Enterprise Version.

Download it at http://www.inbit.com/downloadfullshot.html

Then when it asks you for the registration code, use the keygen to create one and copy and paste the new code.  When the install says to enter an old version serial, use the keygen again to generate a new(old) serial and copy & paste that code into the box.  The install will then finish and you're good to go!
